    • Method Detail

      • deleteTextIndex

        void deleteTextIndex(ResourceIdentifier index,
                     HodJobCallback<DeleteTextIndexResponse> callback)
              throws HodErrorException
        Deletes the given text index using a token proxy provided by a TokenProxyService. This API handles the confirm token returned by HP Haven OnDemand automatically.
        Parameters:
        index - The name of the index
        callback - Callback that will be called with the response
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If a TokenProxyService has not been defined
        HodErrorException - If an error occurs
        HodAuthenticationFailedException - If the token associated with the token proxy has expired

      • deleteTextIndex

        void deleteTextIndex(TokenProxy<?,TokenType.Simple> tokenProxy,
                     ResourceIdentifier index,
                     HodJobCallback<DeleteTextIndexResponse> callback)
              throws HodErrorException
        Deletes the given text index using the given token proxy. This API handles the confirm token returned by HP Haven OnDemand automatically.
        Parameters:
        tokenProxy - The token proxy to use
        index - The name of the index
        callback - Callback that will be called with the response
        Throws:
        HodErrorException - If an error occurs
        HodAuthenticationFailedException - If the token associated with the token proxy has expired
